name: Thirsty
description:
As the days get cooler, all the thoughts of the stars rise.
 Something that never happened, something that will never happen again.
 All of this must be a meaningless worry, but I also become disappointed at myself for not being able to let it go indifferently, yes😉 Am I the only one like that?

 These days, the flow of time is so fast that even if I feel like I'm going in the wrong direction, I decide whether I should be swept away or not.
